Path: godot/classes/class_aabb.rst
Summary: Three constructors for the AABB class: default, from existing AABB, and from position/size vectors.

Constructors:
- AABB() - Creates an empty axis-aligned bounding box
- AABB(from: AABB) - Creates a copy of the provided AABB
- AABB(position: Vector3, size: Vector3) - Creates an AABB with specified position and size vectors
